  # Get Organization by ID
  
  Returns detailed information about a specific organization.
  
  ## Authentication Required
  - HTTP-only cookie with access token
  
  ## URL Parameters
  - `id` (number): Organization ID
  
  ## Access Control
  - Users can only view organizations they belong to
  - **super_admin** can view any organization
  
  ## Response
  Returns complete organization details:
  - Organization ID
  - Name and code
  - Owner information
  - Member count
  - Creation and update dates
  - User's role in the organization
  
  ## Use Cases
  - Organization settings page
  - Member management
  - Organization details modal
  - Audit logs
  
  ## Example
  ```
  GET /api/v1/organizations/1
  GET /api/v1/organizations/42
  ```
}
